docs.lead_paragraph: There was little money in the house. There was less food. The head of the family had been out of work for months and the prospects of employment seemed remote. Debts piled up. Each day was a struggle and wore down little more resistance. Each day seemed harder to bear.

headline.main: TIRED MOTHER KILLS HERSELF AND BABIES; Husband Out of Work, Debts Piling Up, She Gives Up Long Struggle. ASPHYXIATES 2 DAUGHTERS Then Cuts Her Own Throat -- Accountant Finds All His Family Dead.
